data.client_settings: Discord Web App Stable on  Chrome 59 (Stable)
data.short_description: Some pictures don't show up correctly on Chrome 59 (Discord Webapp)
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to <discordapp.com> and use the webapp but make sure you are on Chrome 59 (newest update) - Go to a person in your friends list or a server that has no mutual friends and view their profile - go to mutual friends and wumpus picture will be messed up
